==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: kike
<hw>kike</hw> <pr>(k⟦imac⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A derogatory name
for a <sig>jew</sig>, usually intended and taken as disparaging and
offensive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

